          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Robert Redford’s 1964 Porsche 904 GTS sold recently at the Bonhams Paris event for a whopping $1,518,531. The car was one of the big lot listings, drawing plenty of attention from collectors, enthusiasts, and the media. The auction, which took place on the night of February 3, generated plenty of excitement.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
